      Product Description

      Smart temperature humidity sensor

      • Real-time Update without Delay
      • Free APP Notification Alerts
      • WiFi Remote Monitor, Works with Tuya Smart/Smart Life App
      • Support Voice Control via Alexa
      • / Switchable

      How can i get free app alerts?

      APP Remote Monitoring & Send Notification

      • You can set a smart scene to tigger alerts in the Smart life app.
      • For example, you can set a condition that if the temperature reaches 28 degrees Celsius, the message center on; if the humidity reaches 68%, the message center on.
      • When the temperature/humidity reaches the preset value, you will get free notification alerts through the APP

      High Accuracy

      • Built in Swiss made smart hygrometer sensor, the temperature is accurate to 0.54F while humidity is 5%RH. It provides high precise monitoring.
      • Real-time update without delay,high sensitivity and accuracy, always gives you the latest changes of environment.
      • The Swiss-made sensor monitors the environment reliably and 24/7. Manage the temperature and humidity in the most accurate way.

      Disply on Screen(Time, Date, Temperature, Humidity)

      • Wifi Thermometer Hygrometer has a clock function, you would get a clear view of time and date.
      • You can not only check the current temperature & humidity on the LCD display, but also get current and historic data via the app on your phone.

      Super High Coverage Range

      • Wireless transmission of data signals, mobile phone remote monitoring
      • Free app control (Tuya app /smart life app)
      • The data signals are wireless transmitted, you can remote monitoring through your mobile phone, or control the temperature or humidity by Tuya/Smartlife APP.

      Intelligent Linkage Function

      • Set your smart routine in the app; For instance, when the ambient temperature surpass 30, the air-conditioner open automatically; when the ambient humidity lower 20%RH, the humidifier will spray;automatically turn on your smart wall switch or lighting when the door is opened,ect.
      • As long as the devices are compatible with the Tuya/Smart Life app, you can synchronize more smart devices.

      Unique Design --USB Power Supply, No Battery Required:

      • Our WIFI thermometer and hygrometer power by USB cable,Don't worry about running out of power.
      • Because it is connected to WIFI, under normal circumstances, Temperature and humidity sensors are used 24 hours a day, the battery will run out soon. So we designed it to be without a battery, which saves your money and enables real-time updates of temperature and humidity readings

      Applicable To Various Occasions

      • WiFi Temperature Humidity Monitor can be used indoors and outdoors.
      • Suitable for elderly,children, pets, livestock care and beekeeping, beer, wine and spirits, plants, farms including seeds and bulbs, cellars, greenhouses and even any plant or farm.

      Indoor Hygrometer Thermometer with LCD Display Monitor

      Specification:

      • Free app control: (Tuya APP /Smart life APP )
      • Size: 65*65*17mm(2.6*2.6*0.67in)
      • Micro Input: DC 5V /1 A
      • LED Dictator: Blue
      • Wi-Fi Protocol: 2.4GHz
      • Wi-Fi Standard: IEEE 802. l 1 b/g/n
      • Temperature Measure Range: 0-60
      • Temperature Accuracy: 1
      • Humidity Measure Range: 0% RH~99% IRH
      • Humidity Accuracy:5% RH

      What's in the box?

      • 1* Smart wifi Temperature Humidity sensor
      • 1 *USB Cable
      • 1* User Manual

      Temperature / Unit Switch (Remote Temperature Monitor Support / Reading )

      How to Switch Temperature Units?

      • In two steps:
      • 1. Switch the temperature reading of the App:
      • (1)Open the "Tuya Smart" APP
      • (2)Open the device you set in "All Devices"
      • (3)Click "Set"
      • (4)Click "Temp unit convert" to switch the temperature unit

      • 2. Switch the temperature reading of the device itself:
      • Press the black button on the back of the device once

      • Note: The device's temperature unit cannot be switched through the App. But If you need to switch the temperature unit on the device, please press the reset button once.

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

      Amazon Customer
      4 out of 5 stars
      Decent value indoor temperature and humidity sensor
      Despite poor instructions, I was able to get the device up and running with the Smart Life app and connected to both Alexa and Google Home. For example, I named the sensor Indoor and so say, "Ok Google, Indoor Temperature (or Humidity)?" To change celsius to Fahrenheit, it requires using the Smart Life app and scrolling down until you see Set. If you want to see Fahrenheit on the sensor itself, there's a button under pull-out stand. The sensor does have to be plugged in to USB power all the time but given I was replacing an Eve device that cost four times the price, not a problem. My only complaint is accuracy as it appears to be about a degree and half off the actual temperature.
